quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,Mbega ntazi yuko igihe bazozurwa abari muntatemwa zabo
  100,10,Mugihe hazoserurwa ibiri mubikiriza vyabo
  100,11,Yuko Umuremyi wabo azobamenya neza cane kuri uwo musi ibiremwa vyiwe vyose
  101,1,Ivyago bikubita kumitima y’abantu ariwo muhero w’Isi
  101,2,Ivyo vyago bikubita kumutima y’abantu n’ibihe
  101,3,N’ijambo nyabaki rizo kumenyesha yuko ivyo vyago bikubita kumitima y’abantu nivyahe
  101,4,N’umusi waho abantu bazoba nk’abana b’inzige bashwabagiye hose
  101,5,N’imisozi izoba nk’isufi zasanzajwe zitumukira hejuru
  101,6,Rero uwo k’umunzani wiwe uzoba uremereye
  101,7,Uyo muntu azoba ari mubuzima bumubereye
  101,8,Uwuzoba afise k’umunzani wiwe uhoya hoya
  101,9,"Uyo muntu ubwicaro bwiwe buzoba ari ubwo mumuriro\tudahera witiriwe Hawiyat"
  101,10,None n’ijambo nyabaki rizo kumenyesha uwo muriro witiriwe Hawiyat
  101,11,N’umucanwa waka cane
  102,1,"Mwasamaye\tmukurondera\tubwinshi\tbw’amatungo\tmenshi\tn’ibibondo hamwe n’ukwihayagiza kurivyo"
  102,2,Kugeza aho mugendera intatemwa z’abantu
  102,3,Suko! Ubu vuba muzo menya yuko atarivyo
  102,4,Kandi suko! Ubu vuba muzo menya yuko atarivyo
  102,5,Suko! Iyo mwoba mufise ubumenyi bw’ukuri
  102,6,Mu vy’ukuri muzobona umuriro udahera
  102,7,"Hanyuma, mu vy’ukuri muzo wubona uwo muriro bimwe vy’ukuri"
  102,8,"Hanyuma, mu vy’ukuri muzo bazwa kuri uwo musi kubijanye n’imigisha mwahawe, n’ingene mwayikoresheje"
  103,1,Ndarahiye k’umwanya w’umuhingamo
  103,2,Yuko umuntu ari m’uruhombo
  103,3,"Dukuyemwo\tabemeye\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri,\tn’ukugira\tibikorwa\tvyiza, n’uguhanurana\tmugukurikiza\rukuri,\rn’uguhanurana\tmugufatana\tmunda\rn’ukwihangana"
  104,1,"Ibihano\tbikaze\tcane\tbizoshikira\tuwurigata\tigikanu\tciwe\tn’ugukwiza insaku"
  104,2,N’uwegeranya amatungo yiwe nukuya harura gusa
  104,3,Mbega yiyumvira yuko amatungo yiwe azoyagumana mu buzima bwiwe bwose
  104,4,Oya! ntankeka uyo muntu azo jugunywa mu muriro udahera witiriwe Huttwamat
  104,5,None n’irihe jambo rizo kumenyesha uwo muriro witiriwe Huttwamat
  104,6,N’umuriro w’Imana wakijwe bimwe bikomeye cane
  104,7,Udugira mu mitima y’abantu
  104,8,Mu vy’ukuri uwo muriro udahera abantu babi bazokwugarirwa mwo babe muriwo
  104,9,Kubishitsi v y’ibiti birebire
  105,1,Mbega ntubona ingene Umuremyi wawe yagize abantu bari bafise inzovu
  105,2,Mbega ntiyagize ingeso zabo zononekara
  105,3,Abarungikira inyoni imirwi n’iyindi
  105,4,Zibatera iminana y’ivyondo vyokeje
  105,5,Zibagira nk’ivyatsi vyariwe
  106,1,Kugira ngo aba Quraishi babandanye
  106,2,Babandanya n’ingendo zabo z’igihe c’imbeho n’igihe c’ubushuhe
  106,3,Rero nibasenge nyene icubahiro ciyi nzu yitiriwe Al’kaabat
  106,4,"Ariwe abarisha mugihe c’inzara, n’ukubaha amahoro mugihe c’ubwoba"
  107,1,Mbega wamubonye umwe ahakana idini ry’Imana
  107,2,Uyo n’umwe asunika impfuvyi
  107,3,Kandi ntiyitaho kugaburira aboro
  107,4,Rero ibihano bikaze cane bizoba shikira abantu basenga
  107,5,Batitaho kumategeko y’amasengesho yabo
  107,6,Abagira ivyo bikorwa vyabo kugira ngo biyereka kubantu gusa
  107,7,Nabo n’abima imfashanyo zabo kubazikeneye
  108,1,Mu vy’ukuri twaguhaye imigisha myinshi cane
  108,2,"Rero n’usenge kubera Umuremyi wawe, kandi ubage kubera Umuremyi wawe"
  108,3,Mu vy’ukuri umwansi wawe niwe azoba imfuvyi
  109,1,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  109,2,Jewe si nsenga ivyo musenga
  109,3,Na mwebwe ntimusenga uwo nsenga
  109,4,Kandi sinzo senga ico musenga
  109,5,Namwe ntimuzo senga uwo nsenga
  109,6,"Mwebwe mufise idini ryanyu, nanje mfise idini ryanje"
  110,1,Nihashika intsinzi y’Imana n’ugutsinda
  110,2,Niwabona abantu binjira mw’idini ry’Imana imirwi n’iyindi
  110,3,"Aho rero nusukure n’Umuremyi wawe hamwe nukuyihayagiza, umusabe ikigongwe, mu vy’ukuri niyo yakira ikigongwe"
  111,1,"Hari\tuguhona\tkw’amaboko\tabiri\tya\tAbuu\tlahhabi,\tnawe\takaba yarahonejwe"
  111,2,"Amatungo yiwe ntaco azo mumarira, canke ivyo yaronkeye ngaha kw’Isi"
  111,3,Azo kwinjira mu muriro udahera waka urubeya runiniya cane
  111,4,N’umukenyezi wiwe yatwara inkwi z’urwanko
  111,5,Mw’izosi ry’iwe hariho umugozi uzinshwe
  112,1,"Vuga uti:- niyo Mana imwe rudende gusa"
  112,2,Imana yonyene gusa niyo ikwiriwe kwizigirwa
  112,3,Ntiyavyaye canke ntiyavutse
  112,4,Kandi ntifise uwo bisa nayo n’umwe
  113,1,"Vuga uti:- ndikinze k’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  113,2,N’ishari yivyo yaremye vyose
  113,3,N’ishari ry’umwijima w’ijoro mugihe ryinjiye
  113,4,N’ishari ry’abahuhera mumafundo
  113,5,N’ishari ry’umufise inzigo mugihe agize iyo nzigo
  114,1,"Vuga uti:- ndikinze ku Muremyi w’abantu bose"
  114,2,Umwami w’abantu bose
  114,3,Asengwa n’abantu bose
  114,4,N’ishari ry’uwushira impungenge n’ugusubira inyuma
  114,5,N’uwushiraho izo mpungenge mu mitima y’abantu
  114,6,Nayo ni mubisigo hamwe n’abantu